    <title>使用 Docker + Cashbook 搭建一个私人的记账本</title>
    <url>/2026/01/11/%E7%94%A8%20Docker%20+%20Cashbook%20%E6%90%AD%E5%BB%BA%E4%B8%80%E4%B8%AA%E7%A7%81%E4%BA%BA%E7%9A%84%E8%AE%B0%E8%B4%A6%E6%9C%AC/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h2 id="前言"><a href="#前言" class="headerlink" title="前言"></a>前言</h2><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">        _,met$$$$$gg.          root@raspberrypi</span><br><span class="line">     ,g$$$$$$$$$$$$$$$P.       ----------------</span><br><span class="line">   ,g$$P&quot;&quot;       &quot;&quot;&quot;Y$$.&quot;.     OS: Debian GNU/Linux 13 (trixie) aarch64</span><br><span class="line">  ,$$P&#x27;              `$$$.     Host: Raspberry Pi 5 Model B Rev 1.1</span><br><span class="line">&#x27;,$$P       ,ggs.     `$$b:    Kernel: 6.12.47+rpt-rpi-2712</span><br><span class="line">`d$$&#x27;     ,$P&quot;&#x27;   .    $$$     Uptime: 7 days, 1 hour, 45 mins</span><br><span class="line"> $$P      d$&#x27;     ,    $$P     Packages: 645 (dpkg)</span><br><span class="line"> $$:      $$.   -    ,d$$&#x27;     Shell: bash 5.2.37</span><br><span class="line"> $$;      Y$b._   _,d$P&#x27;       Terminal: /dev/pts/0</span><br><span class="line"> Y$$.    `.`&quot;Y$$$$P&quot;&#x27;          CPU: BCM2712 (4) @ 2.40 GHz</span><br><span class="line"> `$$b      &quot;-.__               GPU: Broadcom bcm2712-vc6 [Integrated]</span><br><span class="line">  `Y$$b                        Memory: 1750 MiB / 8063 MiB</span><br><span class="line">   `Y$$.</span><br><span class="line">     `$$b.                                             </span><br><span class="line">       `Y$$b.                                          </span><br><span class="line">         `&quot;Y$b._</span><br><span class="line">             `&quot;&quot;&quot;&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="为什么选择-Cashbook"><a href="#为什么选择-Cashbook" class="headerlink" title="为什么选择 Cashbook"></a>为什么选择 Cashbook</h2><p>Cashbook 是一个功能全面、设计灵活的账单管理系统，采用前后端分离架构，后端独立管理界面便于系统维护。系统支持用户前台注册，并提供明暗主题切换以优化视觉体验。部署方式采用 Docker，简化了环境配置与发布流程。</p>
<p>核心功能聚焦于多平台账单导入与管理，支持支付宝、微信、京东金融的 CSV 账单文件导入，并可在导入时根据用户配置自动转换消费类型。此外，系统提供模板导入功能，满足个性化数据录入需求。</p>
<p>数据展示方面，系统提供直观的消费日历看板与月度账单分析（未来计划集成 AI 分析）。通过丰富的图表可视化支出类型、支付方式、每日&#x2F;每月流水统计及流水归属，帮助用户清晰掌握财务状况。</p>
<p>系统支持多用户、多账本模式，实现用户间数据隔离与账本间独立管理。数据存储支持 PostgreSQL、MySQL 和 SQLite 多种数据库，并具备账本与系统级别的数据快速导入&#x2F;导出迁移能力。附加功能包括小票图片上传、自助平账（收支抵消）以及共享账本（多用户协同记账）。同时，系统已完成 Web 移动端适配，确保在不同设备上均能流畅使用。</p>
<h2 id="为什么选择-Docker"><a href="#为什么选择-Docker" class="headerlink" title="为什么选择 Docker"></a>为什么选择 Docker</h2><p>Docker 是一个用于开发、交付和运行应用程序的开放平台。</p>
<p>Docker 使您能够将应用程序与基础设施分离，从而可以快速交付软件。</p>
<p>使用 Docker，您可以以管理应用程序的方式来管理基础设施。通过利用 Docker 在交付、测试和部署代码方面的方法，您可以显著减少从编写代码到在生产环境中运行代码的延迟。</p>
<h2 id="准备工作"><a href="#准备工作" class="headerlink" title="准备工作"></a>准备工作</h2><ul>
<li>Docker</li>
<li>Cashbook</li>
<li>Debian Server</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="搭建步骤"><a href="#搭建步骤" class="headerlink" title="搭建步骤"></a>搭建步骤</h2><h3 id="安装-Docker"><a href="#安装-Docker" class="headerlink" title="安装 Docker"></a>安装 Docker</h3><p>删除旧版本的 Docker：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> apt remove $(dpkg --get-selections docker.io docker-compose docker-doc podman-docker containerd runc | <span class="built_in">cut</span> -f1)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>安装新版本的 Docker：</p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Add Docker&#x27;s official GPG key:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> apt update</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> apt install ca-certificates curl</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> install -m 0755 -d /etc/apt/keyrings</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> curl -fsSL https://download.docker.com/linux/debian/gpg -o /etc/apt/keyrings/docker.asc</span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> <span class="built_in">chmod</span> a+r /etc/apt/keyrings/docker.asc</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Add the repository to Apt sources:</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> <span class="built_in">tee</span> /etc/apt/sources.list.d/docker.sources &lt;&lt;<span class="string">EOF</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">Types: deb</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">URIs: https://download.docker.com/linux/debian</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">Suites: $(. /etc/os-release &amp;&amp; echo &quot;$VERSION_CODENAME&quot;)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">Components: stable</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">Signed-By: /etc/apt/keyrings/docker.asc</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">EOF</span></span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">sudo</span> apt update</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h2 id="安装-Cashbook"><a href="#安装-Cashbook" class="headerlink" title="安装 Cashbook"></a>安装 Cashbook</h2><p>使用 Docker Compose：</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">services:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">main:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">container_name:</span> <span class="string">cashbook4</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">depends_on:</span> </span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">&quot;db&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">image:</span> <span class="string">dingdangdog/cashbook:latest</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">restart:</span> <span class="string">always</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># network_mode: &quot;host&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">volumes:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">./data:/app/data</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">environment:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment"># 环境变量详解请查阅：https://doc.cashbook.oldmoon.top/deploy/#cashbook环境变量详解</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment">#NUXT_DATA_PATH: &quot;/app/data&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">DATABASE_URL:</span> <span class="string">&quot;postgresql://postgres:postgres@cashbook_db:5432/cashbook?schema=public&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">NUXT_AUTH_SECRET:</span> <span class="string">&quot;auth_secret&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">NUXT_ADMIN_USERNAME:</span> <span class="string">&quot;admin&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">NUXT_ADMIN_PASSWORD:</span> <span class="string">&quot;fb35e9343a1c095ce1c1d1eb6973dc570953159441c3ee315ecfefb6ed05f4cc&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">ports:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="number">9090</span><span class="string">:9090</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">db:</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">container_name:</span> <span class="string">cashbook_db</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">image:</span> <span class="string">postgres:17.4-alpine3.21</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">restart:</span> <span class="string">always</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment">#network_mode: &quot;host&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># set shared memory limit when using docker-compose</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">shm_size:</span> <span class="string">128mb</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="comment"># or set shared memory limit when deploy via swarm stack</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">volumes:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="string">./db:/var/lib/postgresql/data</span> </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">environment:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="comment">#POSTGRES_USER: postgres # 数据库用户名，不填默认为postgres</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">POSTGRES_PASSWORD:</span> <span class="string">postgres</span> <span class="comment"># 数据库密码 【自行修改！】</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="attr">POSTGRES_DB:</span> <span class="string">cashbook</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">ports:</span></span><br><span class="line">      <span class="bullet">-</span> <span class="number">5432</span><span class="string">:5432</span> <span class="comment">#开发数据库端口，请【自行考虑】</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">docker compose up -d</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>默认管理员用户</th>
<th>默认管理员密码</th>
</tr>
</thead>
<tbody><tr>
<td>admin</td>
<td>admin123456</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
<h2 id="总结"><a href="#总结" class="headerlink" title="总结"></a>总结</h2><p>本文介绍了安装 Docker、安装 Cashbook。</p>
]]></content>
